{"id":"4885f41bf4d8508fa7a66128fae8450fe187b1426ee6d04bbfa9a22aee29bbd0","item_id":"21260b17fd:0","text":"PxrBump 用于为已置换的瓦片提供 secondary bump（次级凹凸）。"}
{"id":"0f1226fba6761d0f52f2dfd63177b9a9c4f0be0b27588aadb276035d48382dbb","item_id":"21260b17fd:1","text":"Bump mapping（凹凸贴图）是一种成本较低的方法，可在不建模细节、也不使用 displacement（置换）改变对象形状的情况下为对象添加细节。这是一种 shading “trick”（着色技巧），由提供的 pattern 产生细节错觉。"}
{"id":"4aa9766177c4d041b5a7d60b5c16e87d3fdf37472d2fdd38b1730f8db933914d","item_id":"21260b17fd:2","text":"这会从 bump map（凹凸贴图，即 scalar displacement map（标量置换贴图），因此只使用第一个通道进行置换）生成 bumped normal（凹凸法线）。凹凸会应用在"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:3","text":"object（对象）"}
{"id":"943a088c84570038282ed9b1bf7b4b6e676b078cb7beac2a172bb6a5fe4a098c","item_id":"21260b17fd:4","text":"space（空间）中。"}
{"id":"2958d416d08aa5a472d7b509036cb7eafd542add84527e66a145ea64cb4cdc75","item_id":"21260b17fd:5","text":"object（对象）"}
{"id":"a529e750ae959a78c356863f3fc843efd652fa76201d7cde719913ec2772f742","item_id":"21260b17fd:6","text":"space（空间）与"}
{"id":"97b0560280ed60a5a1eaa1bc45492543c8a986ad5a25b468c427eb83c3e88191","item_id":"21260b17fd:7","text":"current（当前）"}
{"id":"193cd20006314b60cf5c5bda5f238badd41dddedef39d811da49ca5b1929bee2","item_id":"21260b17fd:8","text":"space（空间）之间的缩放变化会由该节点自动应用。"}
{"id":"d18c93a3074023c66aa3693f2e92aa9faa1fe89bb7f9ac66f01ea9464b2f7e16","item_id":"21260b17fd:9","text":"Texture atlas format（纹理图集格式）文件可以按 UDIM (Mari) 格式或 Mudbox 格式读取。此插件也支持 Rtx procedural texture plugins（Rtx 程序化纹理插件）。"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:10","text":"Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id":"f102986b39effb31080ae442f61febe7ed58df1515c0711ccfadfe0311ccec81","item_id":"21260b17fd:11","text":"Scale（缩放）"}
{"id":"4e65dc7240a3b37f7ed47c1435da897d0654422fa645935ea782c750ff676d12","item_id":"21260b17fd:12","text":"应用到凹凸的 object space（对象空间）Scale（缩放）。"}
{"id":"75081b593d15cf6e631971bc6768723f593b88b172477e40ae7d363e4829816d","item_id":"21260b17fd:13","text":"Disabled（禁用）"}
{"id":"f11b9f862f87d94d73949f877ff77510be0bd86b23d7caf2f482f70d603faf85","item_id":"21260b17fd:14","text":"关闭凹凸效果，便于调试。改用 geometric normal（几何法线）。"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:15","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:16","text":"如果"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:17","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"id":"f68cea4e7febadd22efe7dfea0ef7f97ba2a8de79497735cf643728464a1f54e","item_id":"21260b17fd:18","text":"已连接（并且"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:19","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"20865cfb1f320bb78b17c742d51088fa4ac650c074801eb19289e9601a1250a4","item_id":"21260b17fd:20","text":"未指定），pattern 会执行连接到"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:21","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"id":"78d0cbb65c77d9649c52971c10378eee570b0a8a8edfabf464b7e4ab325a6ab6","item_id":"21260b17fd:22","text":"的上游 pattern network 三次：一次在 shading point（着色点），一次在"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:23","text":"以及"}
{"id":"be7097dd342a707d764703fde533585395209875012be46f7488448dcf830f8d","item_id":"21260b17fd:24","text":" 处。然后对结果做叉乘，以获得 bump normal（凹凸法线）。"}
{"id":"f32d5f3a439d6eff528cf140a07f8cbc73eab4e0faeb8008c0b27a34955a0ab3","item_id":"21260b17fd:25","text":"注意，如果你使用固定 texture（纹理）和 UV，强烈建议使用下面的"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:26","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"28d00ef2a9bc8ea2ccb59bed6687bdf10b1e18e51a5c0fd46f13e024ac268c81","item_id":"21260b17fd:27","text":"参数，因为它会快三倍！"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:28","text":"如果"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:29","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"819cfcd771ec8fd7a65d04e6ca0a7393e37890b3a73cada06062cc606382fbd3","item_id":"21260b17fd:30","text":"已指定，"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:31","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"id":"3c63ef04ef415e76c8179e87c2dc2c3491a0c058b2681c4cf5a357466b948f81","item_id":"21260b17fd:32","text":"会被忽略。"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:33","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"7985094bf7e918f028575a78dee8f885794f240560f112bf0d1d2c58dc9821e2","item_id":"21260b17fd:34","text":"纹理的 filename（文件名）。如果未提供，"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:35","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"id":"75226eacc808872575ff917a7bb831e9db8e91560c5883437b1ea3c4e5b6f2e8","item_id":"21260b17fd:36","text":"会被改用。"}
{"id":"d211cfbcc26a39b757ccaff54a67711fea8441aa5ab674be736e9485327ca039","item_id":"21260b17fd:39","text":"已指定时，pattern 没有连接上游 graph。它会改为从纹理文件中读取 bump value（凹凸值）。输入文件可以是 color（彩色）或 monochrome（单色）文件；如果文件是 RGB，则只会读取单个通道（由"}
{"id":"1e3abf61a37e3cad36b11b459b1cc39e76feb6a0c369fe5270957468288dcc5c","item_id":"21260b17fd:37","text":"如果"}
{"id":"971b974235a86ca628dcc713d6e2e8d975206cc84c858720ce046c2dab72855a","item_id":"21260b17fd:38","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"f006aa17de7681cdae37fe9fccbdbb515dbb50f4b25cb2828479c84f9e96b858","item_id":"21260b17fd:40","text":"First Channel Offset（第一通道偏移）"}
{"id":"ab421bce86230ccc45ee6ec322f868cd8e88b76f336209f97c8478cf7ae09259","item_id":"21260b17fd:41","text":"参数指定）。bump pattern（凹凸图案）会在过滤纹理的同时从纹理取得 derivatives（导数），这与使用"}
{"id":"751a77bbfa814e41098c09534ea937b1230c81bec91f85f05b11df1fb48c2bf0","item_id":"21260b17fd:42","text":"Input Bump（输入凹凸）"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:43","text":"相比具有性能优势。"}
{"id":"fae969a59a309e426969b82a85bd7fb57223b23ea08f6b629906bd6df60d9b4a","item_id":"21260b17fd:44","text":"PxrBump pattern 目前不允许修改纹理的 manifold（流形）；请使用下面的控制项。"}
{"id":"009c03cc4a76f837307874312d0caf4244cd5841133073ccea9f346d65a24048","item_id":"21260b17fd:45","text":"Bump Manifold（凹凸流形）"}
{"id":"fd531854a20458bf6bb4d65b386549690a265ba041cc17d1595a6b73c77a77c5","item_id":"21260b17fd:46","text":"此项接受来自"}
{"id":"b3180962910756fecdd99d178810e38530214de4f79f35c6beb26011807ccf91","item_id":"21260b17fd:47","text":"PxrBumpManifold2D"}
{"id":"dfa8ca3dda7768e23742a8c2ebe2d8c77c7b2ec4ec5e1f97af06df2c120ff0e6","item_id":"21260b17fd:48","text":"Advanced Texture Settings（高级纹理设置）"}
{"id":"8fe14ecc5c2072813ce479fe2eabe100fbb085e782d1ec00a94bc2ef73d0ca8c","item_id":"21260b17fd:49","text":"MIPBias"}
{"id":"ef1ae501cd0e4bef78368c4a97815d65fe62b9950f31f2d4957c2516f2bfea17","item_id":"21260b17fd:50","text":"为渲染选择的 MIP selection（MIP 选择）添加偏移，可选择更高分辨率（负整数）或更低分辨率（正整数）。"}
{"id":"6960e01a00d0599446e00ff16d67c2dda5a8214709238c5b736828bf9540edca","item_id":"21260b17fd:51","text":"MaxResolution"}
{"id":"dd4d9465ab285286fc6fc2dfee9389ce2530e0a69862db3d7484f1cb664f31db","item_id":"21260b17fd:52","text":"将 MIP selection（MIP 选择）限制到首选的最高级别。根据你的选择，这可能会阻止最高分辨率被渲染。"}
{"id":"9f088dbebd6c3c70a5ddbc2c943b11e4ca9acea5757b0b4f2b32479f0dbb747e","item_id":"21260b17fd:53","text":"Advanced（高级）"}
{"id":"5623398d54781bd64929648b12ce690f0a248c8cba6dcd57b88c37559630b38f","item_id":"21260b17fd:54","text":"Input Normal（输入法线）"}
{"id":"1e81d82861e7a023ad3097014e9eaf663e6839437a61673ef6b18ad739cd127d","item_id":"21260b17fd:55","text":"要添加到 bump normal（凹凸法线）上的额外法线。"}
{"id":"5b70861ec6dc456b6edc9821e99435f681a499beee808964c4ae46812225797e","item_id":"21260b17fd:56","text":"Reverse Normal（反转法线）"}
{"id":"820b7d76dc6d2569909ef574f2098fa98d0d55065a74c02dd3291847540e2f49","item_id":"21260b17fd:57","text":"反转结果法线。"}
{"id":"22e51f047f90beac7936ab4aca9ca2269e04e5ca5be52b8d38f9abf5a0c348d3","item_id":"21260b17fd:58","text":"Adjust Amount（调整量）"}
{"id":"f4e9ab18ac9e88ca25ff42b152b8676cb8aaa40ff823355e7fee1f3317bef874","item_id":"21260b17fd:59","text":"当 geometric normals（几何法线）背向摄像机时，用于调整法线的量。当我们在法线中看到裂缝时，这很有用。你可以在"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:60","text":"此处"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:61","text":"找到示例。"}
{"id":"18ee1ea9b251b0a841885c123ba86d48505ac30953edd385a239068d48aa9faa","item_id":"21260b17fd:62","text":"Surface Normal Mix（表面法线混合）"}
{"id":"6f5e90f8ce996a9c442a916227414b1aa03a6755c52b0d7d9751c8e8f1c8ba90","item_id":"21260b17fd:63","text":"将结果法线与原始 surface normals（表面法线）混合的量。趋近 1.0 时会混入更多表面法线。你可以在"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:64","text":"此处"}
{"item_id":"21260b17fd:65","text":"找到示例。"}
{"id":"8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e","item_id":"21260b17fd:66","text":"Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id":"7f69e5947418b1555a1d48ccadf50f5f065a7b50d03def2e60f0470abde48413","item_id":"21260b17fd:67","text":"resultN"}
{"id":"a0cff1de29adcb01a849ee0489d4d936508f384a733425f52237b4f28e65fdcb","item_id":"21260b17fd:68","text":"bumped normal（凹凸法线）。"}
